    - LP: #496816
  * ext4: Split uninitialized extents for direct I/O
    - LP: #496816
  * ext4: Use end_io callback to avoid direct I/O fallback to buffered I/O
    - LP: #496816
  * ext4: async direct IO for holes and fallocate support
    - LP: #496816
